{"tid":801413,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（重開）東京三日兩夜百年食堂+橫須賀之旅","createTime":"2018-08-31T15:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T10:47:40.000Z","uid":21545,"like":15,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6669e625eec53ba8d38d7bdbc35286ece89f2bb0","tid":801413,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"今次主要係東京食咗 前田 鳥がど家 中榮咖喱 同 茂助丸子 呢四間百年食堂 <br />\n去橫須賀除左捉Pok&eacute;mon之外 仲參觀埋三笠號軍艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815f88b6684ff393743231d6a3ff6f8ec11fe8b2","tid":801413,"uid":64374,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c05944d18249b27b30b38a4f50caef6c94c1fcaf","tid":801413,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"第一間 前田 <br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/s.tabelog.com/tokyo/A1311/A131102/13037225/top_amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fs.tabelog.com%2Ftokyo%2FA1311%2FA131102%2F13037225%2Ftop_amp%2F&d=Bdrquyhn7e6gv8Npm%2B5JkJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f3376be1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/s.tabelog.com/tokyo/A1311/A131102/13037225/top_amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n位置：淺草<br />\n<br />\n呢間餐廳 主打滷牛筋同關東煮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我去到嘅時候 關東煮已經賣曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以淨係食咗個滷牛筋。 另外叫咗個天丼set. 埋單1850円 (牛筋600 天丼set $1200 )<br />\n<br />\n講講個牛筋先，佢滷得又諗又入味 真係咬一咬就化開 。味道方面，鹹鹹甜甜咁 真係好惹味 送飯送酒都一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n個天丼就幾特別，因為呢一代老闆娘唔想人食咁鹹 所以個汁明顯係冇平時啲天丼咁濃 好適合香港人口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n分數4.5/5 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老闆對於有香港人知道同專登去佢間鋪佢覺得又驚又喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ace30dbdaa05c11bdd16e62c7df94e8b615120","tid":801413,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:15:04.000Z","msg":"第二間 鳥かど屋 <br />\n呢間主打鰻魚飯 同埋用日本野生鰻魚。 河定海鰻視款式同季節而有所不同<br />\n<br />\n我叫咗一個「梅」鰻重。係用海鰻整嘅<br />\n<br />\n價錢：2400円<br />\n<br />\n鰻魚又香又稔 但係食落又唔油膩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為老板用咗特別嘅方法去煮先再蒸，最後至燒。<br />\n<br />\n另外餐湯唔係一般嘅麵豉湯 係用鰻魚骨熬湯底 再加入鰻魚肝同腸煮成。 <br />\n<br />\n味道同香港食到嘅有所不同 所以唔太推介俾想食濃油赤醬鰻魚嘅香港遊客。若然想試下另一種風格嘅鰻魚飯，呢間會係你嘅好選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n味道：3.5/5 <br />\n<br />\nLink :<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/s.tabelog.com/tokyo/A1301/A130103/13019457/top_amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fs.tabelog.com%2Ftokyo%2FA1301%2FA130103%2F13019457%2Ftop_amp%2F&d=Bdrquyhn7e6gv8Npm%2B5JkJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=122320a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/s.tabelog.com/tokyo/A1301/A130103/13019457/top_amp/</a>"},{"pid":"55891c2e2e5623e31cdd3d282d89aa7ede689644","tid":801413,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"第三間 中榮咖哩屋 <br />\n<br />\n位置：築地市場<br />\n<br />\n我叫咗咖哩汁牛肉汁雙拼飯加叉燒（1100円） 另外買咗咖哩同牛肉汁各一枝返嚟香港（3000円）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/233922_a728f2ce3bc95c96b58565912e04eeb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F233922_a728f2ce3bc95c96b58565912e04eeb3.png&h=b07d5496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n配菜除左一般日本醃菜之外 仲有椰菜絲可以撈落咖哩汁到送飯 味道幾夾唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叉燒分兩種 雞肉同豬肉 我自己覺得豬肉好食啲 因為油香味重啲稔啲 雞肉都稔滑但冇豬肉咁香 另人意外嘅兩款叉燒竟然同咖哩汁好夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咖哩汁 話就話叫印度咖哩 其實係日式咖哩口味 因為佢啲菜已經煮溶曬 所以佢食落去質感十分幼滑 味道更係香醇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牛肉汁個質感同咖哩汁一樣咁幼滑香醇 但味道就好唔一樣 牛膏同蕃茄嘅味道十分突出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 酸酸甜甜幾開胃 <br />\n<br />\n咖哩同牛肉汁雙劍合璧 令人一啖又一啖咁食 唔洗15分鐘就可以食矖一碟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n份量方面 佢碟頭相當大 如果女仔去食 最好帶個男人去 以免食唔曬成浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3db6c584239b898093e7fe171427408a32fff7","tid":801413,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:56:36.000Z","msg":"今日啱啱先係日本返嚟好攰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽晚先繼續打埋最後一間嘅食評 同橫須賀嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370c5976fec668da69e752d5bad517cc55645578","tid":801413,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T16:40:07.000Z","msg":"冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440a9e77a3b4dc161ca5f9f827a2c58edcc08cac","tid":801413,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T17:29:25.000Z","msg":"食物相呢"},{"pid":"fa59a33e31be95c735c019874421157abb8c785c","tid":801413,"uid":47674,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T22:36:22.000Z","msg":"得咖喱有相<br />\n果然係南亞仔"},{"pid":"058200c771ec07734a2a2b9cfb900eefbace3a61","tid":801413,"uid":45332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T22:41:43.000Z","msg":"你去便利店果陣D日本人有冇以為你係店員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.g