19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/130949_d498a6be7e309efd746a54bc64bfdaa7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F130949_d498a6be7e309efd746a54bc64bfdaa7.png&h=1c5e7afc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/130951_6e28be43919f2fa5ec23e7f3d27e804d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F130951_6e28be43919f2fa5ec23e7f3d27e804d.png&h=ee89241d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去咗橫須賀參觀三笠號 真係好壯觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大日本帝國海軍 萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻艦就係當年日清戰爭同日俄戰爭 分別屌打大清同俄仔嘅聯合艦隊旗艦 三笠號<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4e1c3f3b210133cabe661172597a5712b7d8b3","tid":801413,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c05944d18249b27b30b38a4f50caef6c94c1fcaf","tid":801413,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"第一間 前田 <br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/s.tabelog.com/tokyo/A1311/A131102/13037225/top_amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fs.tabelog.com%2Ftokyo%2FA1311%2FA131102%2F13037225%2Ftop_amp%2F&d=Bdrquyhn7e6gv8Npm%2B5JkJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f3376be1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/s.tabelog.com/tokyo/A1311/A131102/13037225/top_amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n位置：淺草<br />\n<br />\n呢間餐廳 主打滷牛筋同關東煮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我去到嘅時候 關東煮已經賣曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以淨係食咗個滷牛筋。 另外叫咗個天丼set. 埋單1850円 (牛筋600 天丼set $1200 )<br />\n<br />\n講講個牛筋先，佢滷得又諗又入味 真係咬一咬就化開 。味道方面，鹹鹹甜甜咁 真係好惹味 送飯送酒都一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n個天丼就幾特別，因為呢一代老闆娘唔想人食咁鹹 所以個汁明顯係冇平時啲天丼咁濃 好適合香港人口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n分數4.5/5 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老闆對於有香港人知道同專登去佢間鋪佢覺得又驚又喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:22:12.000Z","msg":"你唔係南亞人 而家又認香港人 試左sars未？"},{"pid":"a0d7910ed79b25d7f5d12ba62e72b59919400ab9","tid":801413,"uid":37431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab3db6c584239b898093e7fe171427408a32fff7","tid":801413,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:56:36.000Z","msg":"今日啱啱先係日本返嚟好攰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽晚先繼續打埋最後一間嘅食評 同橫須賀嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"冇人想睇呀南亞仔 收皮啦屌你老母 戇鳩鳩出黎柒"},{"pid":"c16eb6629d1d8ccf39e4556d8a6ba7d2d81d6e85","tid":801413,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a0d7910ed79b25d7f5d12ba62e72b59919400ab9","tid":801413,"uid":37431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab3db6c584239b898093e7fe171427408a32fff7","tid":801413,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:56:36.000Z","msg":"今日啱啱先係日本返嚟好攰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽晚先繼續打埋最後一間嘅食評 同橫須賀嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"冇人想睇呀南亞仔 收皮啦屌你老母 戇鳩鳩出黎柒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06: